# QC Analysis

Use this protocol node to review measurement quality and decide whether the workflow should finish or retry preparation.

## Measurement Context

Raw data: {{var|raw_data: json, title = "Raw measurement data"}}

Raw data summary: {{var|raw_data_summary: str, title = "Raw data summary"}}

Measurement quality: {{var|measurement_quality: str = "review", title = "Measurement quality"}}

## QC Decision

Analysis summary: {{var|summary: AiralogyMarkdown = "Initial measurement shows baseline drift and broad peak width.", title = "Analysis summary"}}

Failed metrics: {{var|failed_metrics: list[str], title = "Failed metrics", examples = [["baseline_noise", "peak_width"]]}}

{{check|pass_qc}} Confirm whether the analysis passed QC. The workflow uses this check to choose report or retry.

{{step|review_qc, check=True}} Review failed metrics and decide whether the workflow should proceed to reporting or retry preparation.
